Sentencas: Traditional seals for planar solid oxide fuel cells (pSOFCs) are rigid glass and glass-ceramic, which have caused the problem of being unable to replace malfunctioning components.
Titulo: Novel compressive seals for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Non-glass sealants have become a recent trend.
Titulo: Novel compressive seals for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this paper, fumed silica-infiltrated alumina-silica fiber paper gaskets were investigated as a novel compressive seal for planar solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Novel compressive seals for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The leak rates decreased with increase of the silica-infiltration amount and the compressive load.
Titulo: Novel compressive seals for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Samples pre-stressed at 10 MPa indicated far superior sealing characteristics, with leak rates as low as 0.04 seem cm(-1) at a I MPa compressive stress and a 10 kPa pressure gradient, and 0.05 seem cm(-1) for 0.05 MPa, and a 1.4 kPa pressure gradient.
Titulo: Novel compressive seals for solid oxide fuel cells
